1. There are eighteen subjects in the study.
2. Eleven of the subjects are male.
3. Seven of the subjects are female.
4. The age range of the subjects is 7.8 to 18.2 years.
5. The subjects were randomly assigned to different groups.
6. One group is receiving a placebo.
7. The other group is receiving etanercept.
